<table width="300" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td>
<td valign="top"><font color="#DC320A">OCWC Presentation:</font><br />View slides of OCWC Global 2011 conference keynote speaker Tim O'Reilly. O'Reilly, founder of O'Reilly Media, presented <a href="http://www.slideshare.net/timoreilly/perspectives-on-open" target="_blank"><strong>Perspectives on &quot;Open&quot;</strong></a> at the Conference, which was held in May 2011 in Cambridge, MA, USA.</td>
