	<td colspan="3"><br/>
<span class="orange_title">Health Sciences Portal</span>
<p>
Tufts University has created a dynamic multimedia knowledge management system. Tufts University Sciences Knowledgebase (TUSK) is currently used by Tufts' Medical, Veterinary, Dental and Nutrition Schools as well as three African, one Indian, and three United States medical schools. To learn more about TUSK, 
please click here: <a href="http://tusk.tufts.edu/about/overview/">http://tusk.tufts.edu/about/overview/</a>
</p>
